comments: Wright (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Burke (DAL).
Caboclo (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Burke (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Mejri (DAL) delivers some contact to Wright (MEM) during the screen but Wright is able to play through that contact and continue to defend.
[Observable in enhanced video] Harris releases the inbound within five seconds.
RAR shows Wright (MEM) makes contact to Burke's (DAL) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.

Rabb (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Burke (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harris (DAL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
